In Task 1, which focuses on the visual communication of complex information, I created a polished, high-impact infographic using Prezi. My objective as a Student Digital Ambassador was to reduce the broad notion of digital literacy into five practical pillars for my peers: professional branding, internet safety, foundational definitions, necessary student tools, and appropriate email etiquette.
Using a contemporary color scheme and user-friendly icons, the design highlights a logical, sequential flow that leads the viewer through each subject without overpowering them with text. By laying the theoretical and moral foundation for a responsible online presence, this task sets the stage for the entire portfolio.

